12:37.226 --> 12:38.809
Excuse me, Mrs. Murphy.

12:38.811 --> 12:41.978
<i>Can I talk to you for a minute?
Mrs. Murphy.</i>

12:41.980 --> 12:43.897
<i>Could I just talk with you a moment?</i>

12:43.899 --> 12:46.066
<i>Mrs. Murphy.</i>

12:48.737 --> 12:49.986
Poor woman, huh?

12:51.156 --> 12:53.290
- It's horrible.
- <i>[car engine starts]</i>

13:52.134 --> 13:53.717
Erika.

13:55.354 --> 13:57.187
Loretta. Emily.

13:58.724 --> 14:02.025
We need you to talk john
into talking to the DSD.

14:02.027 --> 14:05.695
John isn't the one that doesn't
want to talk to them, I am.

14:05.697 --> 14:07.864
Why not?

14:07.866 --> 14:10.066
