18:00.348 --> 18:01.681
Just a couple of bottles.

18:01.683 --> 18:03.933
How much are you selling it for?

18:05.303 --> 18:07.220
500 a milliliter.

18:10.142 --> 18:12.642
The samples I took from the
spring that drained are genuine,

18:12.644 --> 18:14.527
So if people are willing
to pay that much,

18:14.529 --> 18:16.946
Then what did I do wrong?

18:16.948 --> 18:19.649
Want to let me take
a look at your hand?

18:19.651 --> 18:21.201
Yeah.

18:21.203 --> 18:23.486
They took my palm print.

18:23.488 --> 18:25.822
Why would they do that?

18:25.824 --> 18:27.907
Can you make a fist?

18:27.909 --> 18:29.375
[winces]

18:29.377 --> 18:31.494
I want a copy of your report.

18:31.496 --> 18:34.714
