when I go in to describe my attackers.

18:36.885 --> 18:41.588
One of them black, 40, clean-cut?

18:43.308 --> 18:45.808
He's the one that hit
you the hardest?

18:49.147 --> 18:51.014
Yeah.

18:51.016 --> 18:53.483
That's john Murphy.

18:53.485 --> 18:56.352
Maybe you let him slide
just this once.

18:59.691 --> 19:01.491
Why would I do that?

19:01.493 --> 19:04.577
Because I have plans tonight
and I don't want to miss them

19:04.579 --> 19:06.946
Because I'm back in here
fixing you up again.

19:11.036 --> 19:13.036
Let me get you some ice.

19:20.095 --> 19:22.045
